{"tid":1558620,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好唔記得八達通","createTime":"2019-09-10T13:54:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T03:13:22.000Z","uid":317795,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"60ab9e12be0da367787af820d75a3d147e13a51a","tid":1558620,"uid":317795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:54:23.000Z","msg":"大家唔好唔記得八達通，八達通公司最大股份本身係地鐵同九廣鐵路，但因為兩鐵合併之後港鐵股份已經接近80%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.octopus.com.hk/tc/corporate/about-octopus/profile/structure/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.octopus.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fcorporate%2Fabout-octopus%2Fprofile%2Fstructure%2Findex.html&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4WqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=37dddfe0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.octopus.com.hk/tc/corporate/about-octopus/profile/structure/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n而八達通係每一條交易記錄都會按比例收費，例如你在Seven買十蚊飲品，可能已經有一蚊去左八達通公司。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.octopus.com.hk/tc/business/faq/octopus-for-businesses/become-octopus-merchant.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.octopus.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fbusiness%2Ffaq%2Foctopus-for-businesses%2Fbecome-octopus-merchant.html&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4WqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=a29b6c9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.octopus.com.hk/tc/business/faq/octopus-for-businesses/become-octopus-merchant.html</a><br />\n(3. 申請成為八達通商戶有甚麼收費？)<br />\n<br />\n所以大家今日起，嘗試坐巴士買野既時候畀現金畀散銀，你咁做唔會傷害到商戶反而令佢地變相賺多左，同時又打撃八達通公司和佢幕後大股東黨錢。大家可能會話一大堆神沙好唔方便，但大家揹慣Gear，神沙令到個袋重少少有乜問題？<br />\n<br />\n今日開始帶番散紙包出街啦。"},{"pid":"bcaf7f94adba1cd55de12062122f4b14a29fbf5a","tid":1558620,"uid":33618,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:16:21.000Z","msg":"大家習慣下用VISA, MASTER嘅pay wave, pay pass<br />\n一樣唔使用散紙"},{"pid":"4e3cb1dec58f9656a998ba9633258c094761185b","tid":1558620,"uid":317795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcaf7f94adba1cd55de12062122f4b14a29fbf5a","tid":1558620,"uid":33618,"like":6,"dislike":0,